data.description: This must see 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in the coveted Goose Creek Subdivision in the northwest section of Wayne County. This home is move in ready and has so many wonderful features including all new paint and carpets! Step into a large entry foyer, formal dining room to the right, spacious kitchen and breakfast nook with lots of counter space. The great room includes a fireplace and has a recessed nook for a large flat screen TV with built in cabinets on the side. Spacious master suite is downstairs with cathedral ceiling, large walk-in-closet, double vanity, jetted soaker tub w/ separate shower. The home also offers two additional spacious bedrooms, a laundry room, lots of storage closets and a large bonus room! The finished bonus room upstairs could be used as a 4th Bedroom or Flex Space. Beautiful raised concrete patio with an additional ground level patio all overlooking a fenced in back yard. Home has Fresh Paint and New Carpet throughout all bedrooms, great room and bonus room. Home has been Professionally Cleaned. This home is minutes from all the major roads, shopping and Seymour Johnson AFB. Seller Offering $6,000 Towards Buyer Closing Costs.  Don't let it slip away.
